lenders.name: YO NO FUI
lenders.occupational_info:
Yo No Fui is an interdisciplinary group working on art and production projects of women in prisons of Buenos Aires, in Argentina, and more recently out of prison, once they have regained their freedom.

This non-govermental organization, a social and civil association , promotes active and specifically the inclusion of marginalized people providing them a place to learn  and produce through workshops of capacitacion, personal expression and production.
In the present there are workshops of serigraphy, encuadernation and book binding, dressmaking, poetry, integrating dance, among other projects.
